register(EventHandler) - Method in class EventManager.EventManager
Method that allow you to register an EventHandler to be able to listen for thrown events This method create EventCaller for every methods in the EventHandler that doesn't contains the NotListening tag and which got an Event related class
registerEvent(Class<? extends Event>, EventHandler, EventCaller) - Method in class EventManager.EventManager
Method that allow you to register an event and use your own EventCaller
registerEvents() - Method in interface EventManager.EventHandler
Method that allow you to register this object to be able to listen for thrown events This method create EventCaller for every methods in this object that doesn't contains the NotListening tag and which got an Event related class
